<i>noun</i>: 흰소리 [힌소리] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>흰소리 [힌소리]</dt><br>
<dd>bluffing; bragging; big talk; hot air</dd><br>
<dd>전혀 근거가 없이 자랑으로 떠벌리거나 잘난 체하며 버릇없이 굴며 허풍을 떠는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>A completely baseless, boastful remark, or bragging while showing off and acting rudely.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>